7 Utes \n|R1=0 |R2=0 |R3=3 |R4=0\n|Home='''No. 10 Huskies'''\n|H1=0 |H2=3 |H3=7 |H4=0\n}}\n{{see also|2018 Pac-12 Football Championship Game|2018 Washington Huskies football team}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Utah Utes|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 1\u201311\n| 2018\n| WASH, 21\u20137\n|}\n{{-}}\n\n===vs. Northwestern (Holiday Bowl)===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road=No. 20 Utes\n|R1=14 |R2=6 |R3=0 |R4=0\n|Home='''Wildcats'''\n|H1=0 |H2=3 |H3=28 |H4=0\n}}\n{{see also|2018 Holiday Bowl|2018 Northwestern Wildcats football team}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Utah Utes|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 1\u20131\n| 1981\n| UTAH, 42\u20130\n|}\n{{-}}\n\n==Rankings==\n{{Further|2018 NCAA Division I FBS football rankings}}\n{{NCAA Division I FBS CFP ranking movements\n| year            = {{2018}}\n| finalpollweek   = -\n| cfpfirstweek    = 9\n| AP_pre          = RV\n| coaches_pre     = RV\n| AP_1            = RV\n| coaches_1       = RV\n| AP_2            = RV\n| coaches_2       = RV\n| AP_3            = RV\n| coaches_3       = RV\n| AP_4            = RV\n| coaches_4       = RV\n| AP_5            = NR\n| coaches_5       = NR\n| AP_6            = RV\n| coaches_6       = RV\n| AP_7            = RV\n| coaches_7       = RV\n| AP_8            = 23\n| coaches_8       = 24\n| AP_9            = 16\n| coaches_9       = 16\n| cfp_9           = 15\n| AP_10           = RV\n| coaches_10      = 24\n| cfp_10          = NR\n| AP_11           = 21\n| coaches_11      = 19\n| cfp_11          = 19\n| AP_12           = 18\n| coaches_12      = 17\n| cfp_12          = 17\n| AP_13           = 17\n| coaches_13      = 17\n| cfp_13          = 17\n| AP_14           = 20\n| coaches_14      = 19\n| cfp_14          = 17\n| AP_15           = RV\n| coaches_15      = RV\n}}\n\n==Players drafted into the NFL==\n{{see also|2019 NFL Draft}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-  style=\"t